            <lb n="c57-0134__main__3"/> 
            <seg xml:id="C28_app253-fMS_end"/>father that my ideas were <seg xml:id="C28_app255-fMS_start"/>deranged â€“ <seg xml:id="C28_app255-fMS_end"/>and <seg xml:id="C28_app257-fMS_start"/>
            <mdel ana="start"/>he<mdel ana="end"/>byinstant<lb n="c57-0134__main__4"/>ly chang<mdel ana="start"/>ed<mdel ana="end"/>ing <seg xml:id="C28_app257-fMS_end"/>the subject of our <seg xml:id="C28_app259-fMS_start"/>conversation <mdel ana="start"/>&amp;<mdel ana="end"/>he<lb n="c57-0134__main__5"/> 
            <seg xml:id="C28_app259-fMS_end"/>endeavoured to alter the course of my thoughts. <seg xml:id="C28_app261-fMS_start"/>
            <lb n="c57-0134__main__6"/> 
            <seg xml:id="C28_app261-fMS_end"/>He wished as much as possible to obliterate the <seg xml:id="C28_app263-fMS_start"/>
            <lb n="c57-0134__main__7"/> 
            <seg xml:id="C28_app263-fMS_end"/>memory of the scenes in <seg xml:id="C28_app267-fMS_start"/>Ireland <seg xml:id="C28_app267-fMS_end"/>
            <seg xml:id="C28_app268-fMS_start"/>and <seg xml:id="C28_app268-fMS_end"/>never <seg xml:id="C28_app270-fMS_start"/>
            <lb n="c57-0134__main__8"/> again <seg xml:id="C28_app270-fMS_end"/>alluded to <seg xml:id="C28_app272-fMS_start"/>them <seg xml:id="C28_app272-fMS_end"/>or suffered me to speak <seg xml:id="C28_app274-fMS_start"/>
            <lb n="c57-0134__main__9"/> 
            <seg xml:id="C28_app274-fMS_end"/>of my <seg xml:id="C28_app276-fMS_start"/>misfortunes. As <seg xml:id="C28_app276-fMS_end"/>time passed away I became <seg xml:id="C28_app278-fMS_start"/>
            <lb n="c57-0134__main__10"/> 
