            <lb n="c57-0134__main__16"/> 
            <seg xml:id="C28_app296-fMS_end"/>desired <seg xml:id="C28_app298-fMS_start"/>sometimes <seg xml:id="C28_app298-fMS_end"/>to declare itself to the <seg xml:id="C28_app300-fMS_start"/>
            <lb n="c57-0134__main__17"/> 
            <seg xml:id="C28_app300-fMS_end"/>whole <seg xml:id="C28_app302-fMS_start"/>world, <seg xml:id="C28_app302-fMS_end"/>&amp; my manners were calmer <lb n="c57-0134__main__18"/>&amp; more composed than they had ever been <seg xml:id="C28_app304-fMS_start"/>
            <lb n="c57-0134__main__19"/> 
            <seg xml:id="C28_app304-fMS_end"/>since my journey to <seg xml:id="C28_app306-fMS_start"/>the Sea of Ice. Even <lb n="c57-0134__main__20"/> my father who watched me as the bird <lb n="c57-0134__main__21"/> does its <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c57-0134__main__d3e25286">n</del> nestling was deceived and thought <lb n="c57-0134__main__22"/> that the black melancholy which had <lb n="c57-0134__main__23"/> oppressed me was quitting me for ever <lb n="c57-0134__main__24"/> and that my native country <seg xml:id="C28_app306-fMS_end"/>
            <seg xml:id="C28_app307-fMS_start"/>&amp; <seg xml:id="C28_app307-fMS_end"/>the <seg xml:id="C28_app309-fMS_start"/>society <lb n="c57-0134__main__25"/> 
            <seg xml:id="C28_app309-fMS_end"/>of <seg xml:id="C28_app311-fMS_start"/>my friends would entirely restore me to <lb n="c57-0134__main__26"/> my former health &amp; vivacity.<milestone unit="tei:p"/>
            <lb n="c57-0134__main__27"/> We <seg xml:id="C28_app311-fMS_end"/>
